{"id":"12624","name":"Set Wallpaper from a Tumblr Blog","tagline":"Easily set your wallpaper from images from a curated Tumblr blog","icon":"ios15 c255 g61581","latest":"34278","description":"\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3>About</h3>\n<p>This shortcut uses Tumblr's random post generator to grab a random post from a specified Tumblr blog. From that post it will pull a random image and set it as your phone's wallpaper. </p>\n<p><strong>Notes:</strong> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>This shortcut works best when the Tumblr is curated with images for your wallpaper. If your blog uses other posts types (text, audio, etc), it will not successfully pull an image. </li>\n<li>This shortcut does not <em>require</em> the Shortcuts app to run, as long as a proper Tumblr blog is specified, it will work. </li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3>Setup</h3>\n<p>To set up your shortcut, you only need to specify 2 items</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Specify the Tumblr blog name</li>\n<li>Specify if you want it to update your Lock screen, Home screen, or both</li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<h3>Support</h3>\n<p>If you need support setting up the shortcut or have ideas/feedback, please reach out to me:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lostcat420\">@lostcat420</a> or <a href=\"https://twitter.com/lostsplat420\">@lostsplat420</a></li>\n<li>Reddit: <a href=\"https://reddit.com/u/lostcat420\">u/lostcat420</a></li>\n<li>Discord: lost cat#4456</li>\n</ul>\n\t\t\t\t","releasenotes":"<p><strong>1.02 - July 26, 2022, 3:33 a.m.</strong></p><p>Fixing setup questions, since they seem to have disappeared</p>"}